    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "From HoTT Require Import Basics Types AbelianGroup AbPullback\n  WildCat.Core Limits.Pullback ReflectiveSubuniverse Truncations.Core.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** * Projective abelian groups *)\n\n(** We define projective abelian groups and show that [P] is projective if and only if every epimorphism [A -> P] merely splits. *)\n\n(** An abelian group [P] is projective if for any map [P -> B] and epimorphism [A -> B], there merely exists a lift [P -> A] making the following triangle commute:\n\n              A\n            ^ |\n         l /  |\n              | e\n         /    |\n              V\n       P ---> B\n          f\n*)\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Class IsAbProjective@{u +} (P : AbGroup@{u}) : Type :=\n  isabprojective : forall (A B : AbGroup@{u}), forall (e : A $-> B),\n    forall (f : P $-> B), IsSurjection e -> merely (exists l : P $-> A, e $o l == f).",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** An abelian group is projective iff epis into it merely split. *)\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Proposition iff_isabprojective_surjections_split (P : AbGroup)\n  : IsAbProjective P\n    <-> (forall A, forall p : A $-> P, IsSurjection p ->\n                           merely (exists s : P $-> A, p $o s == grp_homo_id)).",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": [
        {
          "_type": "goal",
          "name": null,
          "conclusion": "IsAbProjective P <->\n(forall (A : AbGroup) (p : A $-> P),\n IsConnMap (Tr (-1)) p -> merely {s : P $-> A & p $o s == grp_homo_id})",
          "hypotheses": [
            {
              "_type": "hypothesis",
              "names": [
                "P"
              ],
              "body": null,
              "type": "AbGroup"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
